txt.en: You have encountered the dreaded Thangol-ya. This massive Mûmak from Far Harad has seen many battles and lived through them all.
Thangol-ya can be found patrolling Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou have encountered Thangol-ya and should defeat the beast for the good of the Rangers in Southern Ithilien.
You have defeated Thangol-ya and the beast's warband.
Under command to travel to Osgiliath, this massive Mûmak from Far Harad has seen many battles and lived through them all.
Thangol-ya can be found patrolling Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou have encountered Thangol-ya and should defeat the beast for the good of the Rangers in Southern Ithilien.
You have slain Thangol-ya and vanquished a threat to the safety of all that dwell within Southern Ithilien.
You have defeated Thangol-ya and the beast's warband!
